        },
        {
            "title": "日股收漲1028點或1.84% 本周升7.15%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">日股全日穩步揚升，日經平均指數收報56924點，升幅擴大至1028點或1.84%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">本周指數累計升3800點或7.15%。</p>\n</div>",
