            "title": "韓股全日升幅收窄至1.4% 單周漲7.5%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">韓股先揚後回順，南韓首爾綜合指數以接近全日低位收市，報5858點，仍漲80點或1.4%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">指數本周累計則漲408點或7.5%。</p>\n</div>",
