            "title": "台積電上月營收按年升45.2% 首季增長35.1%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">台積電公布，在今年3份合併營收約4151.91億元新台幣，按年升45.2%，較2月份也增加30.7%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">若將今年首3個月合計，台積電季度營收約1.134萬億元新台幣，按年升35.1%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15856353-%e5%8f%b0%e7%a9%8d%e9%9b%bb%e4%b8%8a%e6%9c%88%e7%87%9f%e6%94%b6%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%8d%8745-2-%e9%a6%96%e5%ad%a3%e5%a2%9e%e9%95%b735-1",
